text: This is seo boc to iplanpenne & to doddingtune & to cærswylle the eadwic kyning gebocode æthelhilde on ece yrfe.
Thys synd tha land gemæra to Ipelanpænne & to Doddingtune & to Cærswylle.
Of Mæscumbe on land score on Horsa tor thonon on streame oth Eoth of eoth on pen.
Of pænne on riht land score on lytlan tor thonon on land score to Langandene.
Thonon un land score to thære linde.
Of thære linde to tham beorge.
Thonon to Oddingtorre on landscore to mædercumbe & Cærswellan landscore on tha lace of thære lace on Switheredes stan.
Thonon on herepath to woggan wylle.
Thonon on herpath on tha rode.
Of thære rode on herpath oth tha laca.
Thonne up be streame on mædercumbe on tha wic the tharto hyrth.
